snippet.title: Raiders of the North Sea Digital game trailer
snippet.description:
It's Raiding Season! Plunder your way to Viking adventure in the digital adaptation of the award-winning worker-placement board game!

Coming soon on iOS and Android phones and tablets, PC and Mac on Steam, and Nintendo Switch!
